Implemented `006C2-cultivated-acreage-source-hardening`.

The loan-limit calculation now blocks unresolved BR-020 cultivated-acreage evidence before any assessment, audit, or workflow write. It requires verified selected land holdings, a verified crop plan linked to the same loan application, and agreement across normalized selected-land, crop-plan, and applicable profile cultivated acreage values. Mismatches return `400 VALIDATION_ERROR` with `error.field_errors.cultivated_acreage = "CULTIVATED_ACREAGE_UNRESOLVED"` and preserve existing snapshots on failed reruns.

